  <brief_title>Analysis of HBV-Specific Immune Response in Patients With HBeAg Negative Chronic Hepatitis B Treated With Pegasys (Peginterferon Alfa-2a (40KD)) - Immunology Sub-Study of ML18253</brief_title>
  <official_title>Longitudinal Analysis of HBV-specific T Cell Responses in Patients With HBeAg-negative Chronic Hepatitis B (CHB) Treated With Pegylated Interferon Alfa-2a (40 KD) (Pegasys - RO258310). Immunology Sub-study of ML18253</official_title>
  <sponsors>
